<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Key<sp/>Concepts</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">**GameWorld**<sp/>owns<sp/>all<sp/>GameObjects<sp/>and<sp/>provides<sp/>query<sp/>methods<sp/>for<sp/>component-based<sp/>iteration.<sp/>It<sp/>manages<sp/>the<sp/>lifecycle<sp/>of<sp/>entities<sp/>and<sp/>coordinates<sp/>with<sp/>pools<sp/>and<sp/>managers.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">**GameLoop**<sp/>orchestrates<sp/>the<sp/>frame<sp/>update<sp/>cycle<sp/>through<sp/>three<sp/>phases<sp/>(Pre,<sp/>Main,<sp/>Post),<sp/>each<sp/>containing<sp/>passes<sp/>that<sp/>execute<sp/>systems<sp/>in<sp/>order.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">**CommandBuffer**<sp/>collects<sp/>commands<sp/>during<sp/>a<sp/>phase<sp/>and<sp/>flushes<sp/>them<sp/>to<sp/>dispatchers<sp/>after<sp/>each<sp/>phase<sp/>completes.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">**GameLoopEventBus**<sp/>manages<sp/>phase-level<sp/>and<sp/>pass-level<sp/>event<sp/>propagation<sp/>using<sp/>a<sp/>double-buffer<sp/>pattern.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
